        "# DS 4320 Project 1: Detecting Credit Card Fraud\n",
        "**Author:** Emujin Batzorig  **Pipeline:** Load → SQL Features → Random Forest → Evaluate → Visualize\n",
        "\n",
        "Please upload the 4 tables manually before running the code."
