        "## SummaryThe pipeline demonstrates that a relational four-table dataset enables richer fraud detection features than a single transaction table. The Random Forest achieves **ROC-AUC ≈ 0.82** and **PR-AUC ≈ 0.19** — a 10× lift over the random baseline of 0.02 — by exploiting cross-entity signals like utilisation ratio and geographic distance that are only available through the relational joins."
      ],
